@node "Thumbnails" "Thumbnails"

    @{b}Thumbnails@{ub}

You can use all pictures stored on CD-ROM. To start browsing CD pictures click on
CD-gadget in Options/Graphics or in Edit/Create Mode. If you are using "Try multicolor
first" option colour depth will be depend on screen depth. Otherwise all pictures will
be in 16 colours.

Inside the CD-browse window you can use additional keys:

   up         - move highlighting one item up   (show previous picture)
   down       -                   one item down (show next picture)
   SHIFT+up   -                   ten items up
   SHIFT+down -                   ten items down
   CTRL +up   -                   to first item (show first picture)
   CTRL +down -                   to last  item (show last picture)
   A..Z       -                   to first picture starts with choosen letter
   ESC        - exit from CD-browser without choosing picture
   ENTER      -                      with choosen picture
@endnode

